# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# HELPER COMMENTS (These don't affect functionality)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Color Format Codes:
# \033[0m  = Reset
# \033[1m  = Bold
# \033[4m  = Underlined
# \033[30-37m = Foreground colors (30=black, 31=red, 32=green, 33=yellow, 34=blue, 35=magenta, 36=cyan, 37=white)
# \033[90-97m = Bright foreground colors
# \033[40-47m = Background colors
# \033[100-107m = Bright background colors

# Variable Reference:
# {status}     - Success/error indicator (✓ or ✗ with color)
# {user}       - Current username
# {hostname}   - System hostname
# {cwd}        - Current working directory (shortened)
# {git}        - Git branch info (if in repo)
# {jobs}       - Number of background jobs (if any)
# {arrow}      - Prompt symbol (❯ with color)
# {time}       - Current time (HH:MM:SS)

# Example configurations are in comments above. To use a theme, remove the comment markers.
# Valid theme names must start with their section name, e.g., [theme "mytheme"]
